graph.description: This interaction flow represents the Profit.co login page with email-based authentication and multiple SSO options. The page includes navigation to the sign-up page for new account creation and the home dashboard. Users can enter their email, use SSO options, recover forgotten passwords, or create a new account. After email entry, the interface transitions to show a password input field. Once logged in, users can navigate to various sections including home dashboard, meetings page, and settings page for job titles management using the respective buttons in the left navigation menu.
graph.pageSummary: The Profit.co login page provides multiple authentication methods including email-based login and SSO options for Google, Apple, Slack, and Microsoft. The page features a two-step login process where users first enter their email address, which then reveals a password input field. The page has a clean layout with helpful links for password recovery and new account creation. Users can navigate to the sign-up page (https://app.profit.co/app/p-signup.jsp#/sign-up) by clicking the 'Sign up' link at the bottom of the page. After successful authentication, users can access the home dashboard (https://eu2-app.profit.co/app/ng/profit.jsp#/pr/profit-home/home?at=all) by clicking the Home button in the left navigation menu, access the meetings page (https://eu2-app.profit.co/app/ng/profit.jsp#/pr/meetings) by clicking the Meetings button, or navigate to the job titles management page (https://eu2-app.profit.co/app/ng/profit.jsp#/pr/settings/user-management/job-titles) by clicking the Settings button. The interface includes SSO buttons for quick access through major providers and maintains a user-friendly design with clear instructions and feedback.

graph.description: This interaction flow represents the sign-up page of Profit.co, featuring a comprehensive registration form with multiple sign-up options (Google, Microsoft, or email), required input fields, and footer links including navigation to the Privacy Policy page. The page includes testimonials and awards highlighting the platform's excellence in performance management. graph.pageSummary: The Profit.co sign-up page offers new users multiple registration options while showcasing the platform's achievements and user testimonials. Users can sign up using Google, Microsoft, or email credentials. The page features a clean layout with a header containing the company logo and sign-in option for existing users, a main content area with the registration form, and a footer with legal links including the Privacy Policy and Terms & Conditions. The form collects essential information (name, email, password) and allows users to select their data center location through a dropdown menu that defaults to United States. The page emphasizes the platform's recognition as a leader in performance management with various awards and positive user testimonials from corporate professionals. The page offers a 30-day free trial with no credit card required.
